.SH NOTES

.PP
For security-critical applications, ensure the system has sufficient 
entropy by checking \fB/proc/sys/kernel/random/entropy_avail\fR (should be 
> 1000 for Linux).
.PP
The \fB\-m stats\fR mode displays real-time entropy health monitoring 
and can be used to verify proper system entropy collection.

